{"tid":250682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度女部長倡「以暴易暴」：受害人面前倒吊毆打施暴者","createTime":"2017-05-20T09:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T13:30:26.000Z","uid":105567,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ebe87118f1563a7f75537c705f532dcac3b7e79","tid":250682,"uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:24:27.000Z","msg":"印度不時傳出強暴案，性罪案屢禁不止，更因而被掛上「強姦大國」的惡名，治安問題備受關注。水利部部長巴拉蒂（Uma Bharati）周五（10日）針對這個問題發表驚人言論，指警方處理強暴案件時，應該要在受害人面前，倒轉吊起施暴者嚴刑拷問，直至強暴者請求受害人原諒為止。<br />\n<br />\n巴拉蒂是印度人民黨（BJP）成員，過去多次發表具爭議性的言論，這次也不例外。周五出席北部城市阿格拉（Agra）的集會時，她提到去年7月北方邦一對母女被多名男子集體性侵並拖出汽車一事，指案件並沒得到公正的裁決。她表示：「（警察）必須倒轉吊起強暴者，揮拳毆打他們，然後用鹽和辣椒放在他們的傷口上，直至他們尖叫為止，受害人要看着整個過程。」<br />\n<br />\n要求警方行私刑遭反對<br />\n<br />\n巴拉蒂透露她於2003至2004年擔任中央邦首長期間，曾要求當地警方執法時這樣做。她憶述：「我告訴警察們要倒吊強暴犯和大力毆打他們，要他們大叫痛。我安排受害人隔着警局的玻璃窗觀看過程。當時有警察對我的建議提出反對，我告訴他：『那些犯下兇惡行為的人不能擁有人權，必須把他們的人頭斬下來。』」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/70953/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%A5%B3%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E5%80%A1-%E4%BB%A5%E6%9A%B4%E6%98%93%E6%9A%B4-%E9%81%8F%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA%E9%9D%A2%E5%89%8D%E5%80%92%E5%90%8A%E6%AF%86%E6%89%93%E6%96%BD%E6%9A%B4%E8%80%85?utm_content=buffer9c88b&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F70953%2F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%2580%25A1-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%259A%25B4%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%259A%25B4-%25E9%2581%258F%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A7%25A6-%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%2580%2592%25E5%2590%258A%25E6%25AF%2586%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%2580%2585%3Futm_content%3Dbuffer9c88b%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=61c58766\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/70953/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%A5%B3%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E5%80%A1-%E4%BB%A5%E6%9A%B4%E6%98%93%E6%9A%B4-%E9%81%8F%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA%E9%9D%A2%E5%89%8D%E5%80%92%E5%90%8A%E6%AF%86%E6%89%93%E6%96%BD%E6%9A%B4%E8%80%85?utm_content=buffer9c88b&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a>"},{"pid":"26119d48c1aabb2ed7d12b54cd027350af4a789b","tid":250682,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:36:23.000Z","msg":"SM上腦？"},{"pid":"9233e534890ff528c09cedbceac4cd3807527947","tid":250682,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:37:52.000Z","msg":"讚成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c66abee429a97f78e678721664780646b15afc","tid":250682,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T09:41:36.000Z","msg":"多鳩餘, 喺佢地啲咁嘅國家咪又係變成警察貪污行私刑扮執法, 有錢人照脫罪窮人倒吊含撚<br />\n佢以為佢地國家強姦案多係因為刑罰唔夠重?"},{"pid":"27a74ed30fd2ff65b6c91c11d19a73006eca9f39","tid":250682,"uid":101390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:15:53.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家只能用垃圾方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f2bf54d058ac0132617b83d694da723d39bac1","tid":250682,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:16:47.000Z","msg":"女部長好快比人姦殺碎屍"},{"pid":"e177569e091007c8d5c9bb0f150c24600ee31d77","tid":250682,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:42:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91be63c23c3ab9416df2487d6fad60d28b89a4a1","tid":250682,"uid":34203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T12:49:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女部長好快比人姦殺碎屍</blockquote><br />\n咁都姦得落 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a11e6d7b11c979540e8af9061362936a00fd58","tid":250682,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"